{"tid":990210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#131: 生田絵梨花 2nd写真集「インターミッション」1月22日正式發售","createTime":"2019-01-21T11:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T12:03:04.000Z","uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f885292a77d6088e03f2ccea6d07212b8a969e4e","tid":990210,"uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:54:24.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">LIHK乃PO呼籲: <br />\n花花你都係著返件衫啦<br />\n<strong></strong></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SwoO61D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSwoO61D.png&h=5ac8dcf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一期生,二期生,三期生以及四期生在內，團體目前共有48名成員，而隊長為櫻井玲香。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團體名稱中的「乃木坂」是唱片公司日本索尼音樂（SME）總部大樓的所在地。<br />\n根據秋元康所說，<span style=\"color: red;\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成員名單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nogizaka46.com%2Fmember%2F&d=cyeyiWh7%2Feu%2BrCQK0yGmkRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=45d7c6ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">-NEWS-</div><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 生田絵梨花 2nd写真集「インターミッション」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1月22日正式發售</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tok5x5r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTok5x5r.png&h=50b70e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 北野日奈子ファースト写真集 「空気の色」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gPlzise.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgPlzise.jpg&h=379fa89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 井上小百合ファースト写真集 「存在」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cdBjIT6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcdBjIT6.jpg&h=c461748b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 22ndシングル<br />\n「帰り道は遠回りしたくなる」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2GkiUls.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2GkiUls.jpg&h=a5ad3116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46成員列表 22.5ND VER.(最新)</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pn8GgE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pn8GgE.png&h=e18452c4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46 四期生</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NjUnHMj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNjUnHMj.jpg&h=61687ed4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnogizaka46-dc.com%2Fsort%2F&d=cyeyiWh7%2Feu%2BrCQK0yGmkRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=83c0e4c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購,，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員,但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本參加握手會、演唱會，但不要幻想他會再來港，因香港已經柒出國際。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦?<br />\nNONE<br />\n<br />\n6）長期置頂<br />\n<br />\n奶po5周年犯罪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/faFIKx7SJevQlnT73\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FfaFIKx7SJevQlnT73&d=cyeyiWh7%2Feu%2BrCQK0yGmkRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d7dee900\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/faFIKx7SJevQlnT73</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 強烈歡迎絲打參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1月31號截<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TEMPLATE:</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=cyeyiWh7%2Feu%2BrCQK0yGmkRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=253882bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"fc33e6660a93e32f28a7dc2bfe2f76ebde40b01e","tid":990210,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sSugOsX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsSugOsX.jpg&h=92aa47e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真.生田繪梨花老公留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝老婆生日快樂+寫真大賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11410a38571a9bec429a856a3f9a7475d706eb0","tid":990210,"uid":87229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/syQsaGk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsyQsaGk.png&h=4a05c3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無喇喇抽中桃子 唔中花花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 留名"},{"pid":"0ebb79f44408bc0346eabce321042ff5fc166687","tid":990210,"uid":87229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:56:06.000Z","msg":"一個神偷1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b77ffbb2ff90eaa6527f7ba2744158412c09ae0","tid":990210,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/55a0vGA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55a0vGA.png&h=220efa3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9Ec6eW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9Ec6eW.png&h=eb426b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢二張生蛋海報原來係香港攪"},{"pid":"ef4f2c7ca1eb423bc29f3d8db3c1e611d22cfa47","tid":990210,"uid":63295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"唔祝埋花花生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75718efbf47cd3288ad9566ed25cb3400bf4d498","ti